The '''High Council''' was a body in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. Among its many functions, it received reports from the [[New Republic Observer]]s, a governmental group that investigated potentially improper governmental activities. It also had a large say in matters of diplomacy and military deployment.

The High Council was formed of the leading members of the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]], including the [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]], and sat in curved, elevated dias at the end of the Senate. During the [[Caamas Document Crisis]], members of the High Council included [[Ponc Gavrisom]], [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]], [[Borsk Fey'lya]], and [[Sien Siev]]. During the crisis, a majority of the High Council opposed the continued relationship with the [[Smugglers' Alliance]], and at least three councilors took an anti-[[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] stance.

It possibly formed some type of basis for the later [[High Council (Galactic Alliance)|High Council]] of the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]].

